    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断追求真实感的3D格斗游戏始祖“Virtua Fighter”，终于登陆Steam。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/4a73410f1d417ed3e78b85635687343d.poster.avif?t=1769739453\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/4a73410f1d417ed3e78b85635687343d.webm?t=1769739453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/4a73410f1d417ed3e78b85635687343d.mp4?t=1769739453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作将支持不受平台限制的跨平台游玩功能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，为实现与全世界玩家进行更加流畅、更有深度的对战，本作也将支持回滚设定网络代码功能。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与全世界的玩家享受白热化的战斗吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/95ba2bcadace81f1c3077221198500b4.poster.avif?t=1769739453\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/95ba2bcadace81f1c3077221198500b4.webm?t=1769739453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/95ba2bcadace81f1c3077221198500b4.mp4?t=1769739453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除此之外，能够与全世界强者进行切磋的单人专属全新模式“World Stage”登场！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“World Stage”模式中，来自世界各地的众多强者将齐聚一堂！同时，真实存在的知名玩家也将化身CPU登场其中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与充满个性的对手们战斗磨练技巧，以成为最强为目标吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他更有回放功能的追加、训练功能的改善等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/093f305f814cb49d5a336d31a58cbbfa.poster.avif?t=1769739453\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/093f305f814cb49d5a336d31a58cbbfa.webm?t=1769739453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112260/extras/093f305f814cb49d5a336d31a58cbbfa.mp4?t=1769739453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是初次游玩Virtua Fighter的新玩家，还是重返游戏的老玩家，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辅助功能充实可靠的“Virtua Fighter”决定版在此等待着您的到来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※本商品仅包含游戏本体。除本商品外，还存在包含游戏本体和追加内容的套装商品，请注意避免重复购买。</p>",
